1
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:34,918
=Vanished Name=

2
00:01:35,224 --> 00:01:37,560
=Episode 14=
(Her Breath)

3
00:01:38,264 --> 00:01:40,410
(2006, La City)

4
00:01:40,410 --> 00:01:41,329
Ren Meiyan.

5
00:01:42,329 --> 00:01:43,369
Sun Jinfu has been caught.

6
00:01:44,650 --> 00:01:47,089
I want my dad.

7
00:01:47,410 --> 00:01:49,889
I want my dad.

8
00:01:52,570 --> 00:01:55,010
I want my dad.

9
00:02:18,209 --> 00:02:19,290
It's sold so quickly.

10
00:02:29,209 --> 00:02:32,449
People say
a couple separates in a crisis.

11
00:02:32,889 --> 00:02:35,769
You quickly sold this house
right after he left.

12
00:02:44,250 --> 00:02:47,449
Why didn't you tell us earlier
that he had deeded you the house?

13
00:03:18,850 --> 00:03:20,850
Excuse me, is Yuanyuan here?

14
00:03:21,209 --> 00:03:22,929
Mom!

15
00:03:25,049 --> 00:03:25,570
Yuanyuan.

16
00:03:25,570 --> 00:03:27,370
You're finally here!

17
00:03:28,090 --> 00:03:29,049
Yuanyuan, don't cry.

18
00:03:29,769 --> 00:03:31,049
I got a lollipop for you.

19
00:03:38,169 --> 00:03:40,530
The police investigated the case.

20
00:03:41,329 --> 00:03:43,570
I'm innocent, so they let me go.

21
00:03:45,570 --> 00:03:47,850
Thank you for taking care of Yuanyuan.

22
00:03:48,370 --> 00:03:50,769
Not at all.
After all, we're both mothers.

23
00:03:52,290 --> 00:03:55,130
I don't think
we'll see each other again.

24
00:03:55,410 --> 00:03:56,169
Take care.

25
00:03:56,810 --> 00:03:57,410
Take care.

26
00:03:58,209 --> 00:03:59,889
Yuanyuan, let's go.

27
00:04:01,410 --> 00:04:02,130
Xiaofei.

28
00:04:07,769 --> 00:04:10,329
This model is your favorite.

29
00:04:10,729 --> 00:04:13,250
I don't like it that much.
You take it back.

30
00:04:17,649 --> 00:04:20,170
Before, I ate lollipops,

31
00:04:20,570 --> 00:04:21,730
deliberately tempting you.

32
00:04:22,130 --> 00:04:23,130
That was wrong of me.

33
00:04:24,649 --> 00:04:26,370
I'm giving you this lollipop.

34
00:04:26,690 --> 00:04:27,250
From now on,

35
00:04:28,250 --> 00:04:31,329
whenever you eat a lollipop,
you'll think of me.

36
00:04:32,529 --> 00:04:35,529
Xiaoming, don't forget me.

37
00:04:37,449 --> 00:04:38,570
I won't forget you.

38
00:04:55,089 --> 00:04:55,730
Sir.

39
00:04:56,329 --> 00:04:59,610
This is to pay some
of the money Sun Jinfu owed.

40
00:05:00,649 --> 00:05:02,529
I know he owed millions of yuan.

41
00:05:02,584 --> 00:05:03,930
It's a few hundred thousand yuan,

42
00:05:04,930 --> 00:05:06,849
but it's all the savings we have.

43
00:05:07,930 --> 00:05:10,769
I thought paying back some
might reduce his sentence,

44
00:05:11,209 --> 00:05:13,050
like one month less,

45
00:05:13,849 --> 00:05:15,529
or even just one day less.

46
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,064
(Repaying Sun Jinfu's debt
of 570,000 yuan, by Ren Meiyan)

47
00:05:24,610 --> 00:05:25,289
Xiaoming.

48
00:05:25,289 --> 00:05:26,130
(2023, Qidaohezi)

49
00:05:26,130 --> 00:05:27,529
My dad is grateful to you.

50
00:05:27,969 --> 00:05:30,289
If Ms. Ren hadn't sold her house

51
00:05:30,529 --> 00:05:31,810
to pay some of his debt,

52
00:05:32,529 --> 00:05:34,289
he'd still be in prison now.

53
00:05:38,529 --> 00:05:40,050
Why bring that up?

54
00:05:40,930 --> 00:05:43,490
These past few years,
he hasn't gone to see you

55
00:05:44,409 --> 00:05:45,529
or allowed me to visit you.

56
00:05:45,849 --> 00:05:47,409
He was afraid of disrupting your life.

57
00:05:50,849 --> 00:05:53,050
You just mentioned family abuse...

58
00:05:53,930 --> 00:05:54,849
It's not about me.

59
00:05:57,370 --> 00:06:00,209
It's about my teacher's daughter.

60
00:06:01,170 --> 00:06:02,370
My teacher passed away.

61
00:06:03,329 --> 00:06:04,889
Her husband abuses the child.

62
00:06:05,649 --> 00:06:08,370
I want to find a way
to get that child out.

63
00:06:11,649 --> 00:06:13,010
She is not in our jurisdiction?

64
00:06:13,050 --> 00:06:13,610
No.

65
00:06:13,930 --> 00:06:14,610
How about this?

66
00:06:16,409 --> 00:06:17,849
Tell me her details.

67
00:06:18,449 --> 00:06:21,170
If I verify the situation is real,

68
00:06:21,370 --> 00:06:22,289
it'll be resolved.

69
00:06:24,810 --> 00:06:25,649
What's her name?

70
00:06:29,130 --> 00:06:29,969
I'm taking this call.

71
00:06:33,690 --> 00:06:34,449
What's up, Xiaofei?

72
00:06:34,690 --> 00:06:37,130
Xiaoming, Mom is missing!

73
00:06:37,370 --> 00:06:38,370
Come back quickly!

74
00:06:40,130 --> 00:06:42,649
Find Mom. Mom is gone!

75
00:06:43,170 --> 00:06:44,010
Don't panic.

76
00:06:44,969 --> 00:06:45,769
Check the wardrobe.

77
00:06:45,944 --> 00:06:46,810
Is her stuff inside?

78
00:06:52,649 --> 00:06:55,209
The suitcase and her down coat are gone.

79
00:06:57,370 --> 00:06:58,889
Alright, I know where she is.

80
00:06:59,544 --> 00:07:00,969
(Tubao Village)
Yuxiu, you said you were fine.

81
00:07:00,969 --> 00:07:02,889
If you touch my wife's grave,
I'll kill you.

82
00:07:02,889 --> 00:07:03,416
You beast!

83
00:07:03,416 --> 00:07:04,250
What are you doing?

84
00:07:04,250 --> 00:07:04,849
Stop!

85
00:07:05,170 --> 00:07:06,649
- You ruined her life.
- Kill her!

86
00:07:06,649 --> 00:07:07,649
- Police!
- Kill her!

87
00:07:07,730 --> 00:07:08,289
(Wen Yuxiu's Tomb)
Police!

88
00:07:08,289 --> 00:07:09,050
Call the police!

89
00:07:09,170 --> 00:07:09,810
Put it down!

90
00:07:09,810 --> 00:07:10,529
Call the police!

91
00:07:12,170 --> 00:07:13,209
- Stay away!
- Let go!

92
00:07:13,209 --> 00:07:14,610
I'm killing you. You harmed Yuxiu!

93
00:07:16,010 --> 00:07:17,010
You killed her!

94
00:07:17,930 --> 00:07:18,649
He is the killer.

95
00:07:19,690 --> 00:07:20,930
I'm going to kill you!

96
00:07:21,170 --> 00:07:23,050
You killed her.
You deserve to die horribly!

97
00:07:23,050 --> 00:07:23,769
Nonsense!

98
00:07:23,769 --> 00:07:24,849
I'll dig up the grave.

99
00:07:25,649 --> 00:07:27,170
I want an autopsy.

100
00:07:27,329 --> 00:07:28,769
I want to file a report.

101
00:07:28,849 --> 00:07:30,130
Nonsense!

102
00:07:30,209 --> 00:07:30,810
Calm down!

103
00:07:31,010 --> 00:07:32,010
Kill you!

104
00:07:32,449 --> 00:07:34,170
I want an autopsy.

105
00:07:34,209 --> 00:07:35,130
Ren Meiyan!

106
00:07:35,690 --> 00:07:37,969
You're suspected
of destroying someone else's grave,

107
00:07:38,209 --> 00:07:39,050
disturbing the peace.

108
00:07:39,329 --> 00:07:39,969
Take her away.

109
00:07:40,050 --> 00:07:40,810
Okay.

110
00:07:40,810 --> 00:07:41,969
I protest!

111
00:07:42,329 --> 00:07:43,209
Come on, Ms. Ren.

112
00:07:43,409 --> 00:07:44,289
He is guilty!

113
00:07:44,289 --> 00:07:45,449
Kill her!

114
00:07:45,610 --> 00:07:46,529
Come with me.

115
00:07:46,570 --> 00:07:47,409
Come on, Ms. Ren.

116
00:07:47,730 --> 00:07:48,370
Freeze!

117
00:07:49,130 --> 00:07:50,370
Don't let him go.

118
00:07:50,449 --> 00:07:51,769
Don't let him go.

119
00:07:52,529 --> 00:07:55,170
Hao Ying killed Wen Yuxiu.

120
00:07:55,170 --> 00:07:56,329
Ms. Ren, I'm protecting you.

121
00:07:56,329 --> 00:07:56,969
Get out of here.

122
00:07:56,969 --> 00:07:57,624
Go!

123
00:07:57,730 --> 00:07:58,649
Why catch me?

124
00:07:58,649 --> 00:07:59,329
Step back!

125
00:07:59,329 --> 00:08:00,250
I'm protecting you.

126
00:08:00,250 --> 00:08:01,170
It's dangerous here.

127
00:08:02,610 --> 00:08:05,370
Hao Ying killed Wen Yuxiu.

128
00:08:05,769 --> 00:08:07,529
Believe me. He is a bad person.

129
00:08:08,370 --> 00:08:10,170
Don't worry. I'll investigate this.

130
00:08:11,050 --> 00:08:11,730
Step back!

131
00:08:29,730 --> 00:08:31,096
Hey, Xiaoming.

132
00:08:33,850 --> 00:08:35,169
No worries. Everything's fine.

133
00:08:35,450 --> 00:08:36,929
I've already calmed Ms. Ren.

134
00:08:36,970 --> 00:08:38,450
I'll take her back tomorrow.

135
00:08:41,330 --> 00:08:42,730
That's okay.

136
00:08:43,169 --> 00:08:44,569
Okay, we'll talk when I get back.

137
00:08:54,529 --> 00:08:57,809
Ms. Ren, destroying someone else's grave
is really illegal.

138
00:08:58,049 --> 00:09:01,169
You can't just act impulsively.

139
00:09:02,049 --> 00:09:02,730
Officer Li.

140
00:09:04,010 --> 00:09:05,569
My mind is clear.

141
00:09:06,409 --> 00:09:08,049
I know what I'm doing.

142
00:09:08,912 --> 00:09:09,912
I want to report a case.

143
00:09:10,689 --> 00:09:11,970
You help me investigate it.

144
00:09:13,010 --> 00:09:14,889
Then tell me.

145
00:09:15,210 --> 00:09:18,169
Why do you say
Hao Ying killed Wen Yuxiu?

146
00:09:20,250 --> 00:09:23,490
These days,
I dream about her every night.

147
00:09:24,649 --> 00:09:26,490
As soon as I close my eyes,

148
00:09:26,929 --> 00:09:28,769
she comes to talk to me.

149
00:09:31,169 --> 00:09:33,689
She says we will meet soon.

150
00:09:35,809 --> 00:09:37,130
She doesn't want to be here.

151
00:09:38,649 --> 00:09:41,010
She told me to take her home.

152
00:09:42,409 --> 00:09:44,929
I promised her,
and I will make it happen.

153
00:09:48,210 --> 00:09:49,569
What I'm saying is true.

154
00:09:50,169 --> 00:09:51,730
She was killed by Hao Ying.

155
00:09:52,409 --> 00:09:53,450
You have to believe me.

156
00:09:54,809 --> 00:09:57,169
Ms. Ren, you also need to trust us.

157
00:09:57,809 --> 00:10:00,649
Rest assured.
I'll get to the bottom of this case.

158
00:10:05,010 --> 00:10:06,649
Yanzi, get some water for Ms. Ren.

159
00:10:08,769 --> 00:10:09,330
Hello?

160
00:10:11,289 --> 00:10:12,130
Have some water.

161
00:10:12,330 --> 00:10:14,289
What? Hao Ying is dead?

162
00:10:29,336 --> 00:10:29,970
Step aside.

163
00:10:29,970 --> 00:10:31,049
Ma'am, step aside, please.

164
00:10:31,330 --> 00:10:32,010
Step aside.

165
00:10:32,024 --> 00:10:32,649
Come on.

166
00:10:32,649 --> 00:10:33,569
Step aside.

167
00:10:34,250 --> 00:10:34,809
Captain Li.

168
00:10:36,529 --> 00:10:38,424
Chen, how is it?

169
00:10:39,169 --> 00:10:40,010
Why is she here?

170
00:10:40,649 --> 00:10:42,370
I'm worried about her
if I leave her alone.

171
00:10:42,490 --> 00:10:44,130
Having her under my watch is safe.

172
00:10:44,569 --> 00:10:45,370
What happened?

173
00:10:46,450 --> 00:10:47,610
Hao Ying set the fire.

174
00:10:48,529 --> 00:10:49,529
Why did he set a fire?

175
00:10:50,370 --> 00:10:53,130
People from the Women's Federation
found him for Yamei.

176
00:10:53,409 --> 00:10:54,529
But he didn't open the door.

177
00:10:54,850 --> 00:10:56,010
He threatened to set a fire.

178
00:10:56,370 --> 00:10:57,569
And he actually did it.

179
00:10:58,130 --> 00:10:59,169
Luckily, Yamei ran fast.

180
00:10:59,409 --> 00:11:00,850
The Women's Federation saved her.

181
00:11:03,210 --> 00:11:04,169
This is Hao Ying's kid.

182
00:11:04,809 --> 00:11:06,090
Everyone calls her Yamei.

183
00:11:14,010 --> 00:11:14,730
How pitiful.

184
00:11:17,490 --> 00:11:18,169
It's okay.

185
00:11:20,210 --> 00:11:21,850
Are you Wen Yuxiu's daughter?

186
00:11:25,250 --> 00:11:26,370
What's your name?

187
00:11:28,649 --> 00:11:29,569
How old are you?

188
00:11:31,330 --> 00:11:33,929
She can't speak or hear.

189
00:12:02,929 --> 00:12:05,490
Since the house is burned down,
how is there still electricity?

190
00:12:05,490 --> 00:12:06,409
This light is still on.

191
00:12:07,169 --> 00:12:09,490
The main house and the woodshed
aren't on the same circuit.

192
00:12:09,730 --> 00:12:10,610
Same with my house.

193
00:12:10,776 --> 00:12:11,409
Right.

194
00:12:11,409 --> 00:12:13,049
Same with my house.

195
00:12:13,049 --> 00:12:13,976
On a different circuit?

196
00:12:13,976 --> 00:12:14,689
Sure.

197
00:12:15,210 --> 00:12:15,850
Let me see.

198
00:12:21,889 --> 00:12:23,529
See? Their house is haunted.

199
00:12:23,689 --> 00:12:25,450
Look at that bulb. It's flickering.

200
00:12:25,850 --> 00:12:27,010
I saw it last time too.

201
00:12:27,450 --> 00:12:28,370
Exactly.

202
00:13:17,370 --> 00:13:18,289
Who's down there?

203
00:13:20,049 --> 00:13:21,409
Who's down there? Make a sound.

204
00:13:21,689 --> 00:13:22,529
Make a sound.

205
00:13:30,929 --> 00:13:31,970
Bring an axe.

206
00:13:34,169 --> 00:13:35,730
Bring an axe.

207
00:13:39,569 --> 00:13:40,250
Where is it?

208
00:13:41,409 --> 00:13:42,169
This lock.

209
00:14:28,649 --> 00:14:30,250
Yuxiu.

210
00:14:45,560 --> 00:14:49,240
(Qidaohezi)

211
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,744
(Qidaohezi People's Hospital)

212
00:16:10,889 --> 00:16:13,130
Yamei has been settled
by the Women's Federation.

213
00:16:13,330 --> 00:16:14,929
You and your mom can rest assured.

214
00:16:16,330 --> 00:16:17,130
Thank you.

215
00:16:17,809 --> 00:16:19,130
Don't mention it.

216
00:16:20,929 --> 00:16:22,889
Don't worry. Everything will get better.

217
00:16:24,889 --> 00:16:27,889
After Hao Ying took Wen Yuxiu home,
he locked her up for a while.

218
00:16:28,169 --> 00:16:31,010
Hao Ying thought she wouldn't run away
after making her pregnant.

219
00:16:31,610 --> 00:16:33,049
I've seen her letters to the Wens.

220
00:16:33,970 --> 00:16:35,130
Unexpectedly,

221
00:16:35,169 --> 00:16:37,929
in 2006, Wen Yuxiu
developed health problems.

222
00:16:39,130 --> 00:16:40,370
(2006, Shabei County)
I'm kind of shocked.

223
00:16:41,490 --> 00:16:42,769
You're menopausal at this age.

224
00:16:44,370 --> 00:16:45,016
What?

225
00:16:46,730 --> 00:16:47,730
Can she get pregnant?

226
00:16:47,970 --> 00:16:49,010
No, she can't.

227
00:16:49,569 --> 00:16:50,569
That's awful. I...

228
00:16:50,850 --> 00:16:52,370
I want children.

229
00:16:52,569 --> 00:16:54,169
But your wife has been menopausal.

230
00:17:55,569 --> 00:17:57,809
Later, Hao Ying brought back
a woman named Liu Mei.

231
00:17:58,609 --> 00:18:00,809
The local police
are checking Liu Mei's background.

232
00:18:01,609 --> 00:18:03,410
Liu Mei likely
has intellectual disabilities.

233
00:18:03,930 --> 00:18:04,690
She might be lost.

234
00:18:05,809 --> 00:18:07,609
At the time,
she was eight months pregnant.

235
00:18:08,010 --> 00:18:08,609
Pregnant?

236
00:18:09,769 --> 00:18:10,369
Yamei?

237
00:18:13,289 --> 00:18:15,129
Hao Ying is not
Yamei's biological father.

238
00:18:15,410 --> 00:18:17,569
Hao Ying hoped Liu Mei would have a son.

239
00:18:18,490 --> 00:18:20,170
When Hao Ying took Liu Mei

240
00:18:20,170 --> 00:18:21,730
to the clinic for prenatal checkups,

241
00:18:21,970 --> 00:18:23,369
he filled in Wen Yuxiu's name.

242
00:18:24,769 --> 00:18:27,129
Did Liu Mei know
Ms. Zhou was locked in the cellar?

243
00:18:29,730 --> 00:18:30,849
It was because of Liu Mei

244
00:18:30,930 --> 00:18:33,450
that we could see Wen Yuxiu's writings.

245
00:18:34,264 --> 00:18:37,010
(2006, Hao Ying's Cellar, Tubao Village)

246
00:18:37,010 --> 00:18:37,624
Get up.

247
00:18:38,170 --> 00:18:38,930
What are you doing?

248
00:18:38,930 --> 00:18:39,512
Don't hit her.

249
00:18:39,650 --> 00:18:40,450
Stop hitting her!

250
00:18:41,464 --> 00:18:42,769
It hurts!

251
00:18:43,730 --> 00:18:44,690
- I'll kill you!
- Stop!

252
00:18:44,930 --> 00:18:45,569
Hao.

253
00:18:46,129 --> 00:18:46,809
Stop hitting her.

254
00:18:47,129 --> 00:18:48,450
Her belly is so big.

255
00:18:48,609 --> 00:18:49,144
So what?

256
00:18:50,129 --> 00:18:51,210
Stop it! Stop hitting her!

257
00:18:51,609 --> 00:18:53,369
Be careful you don't lose the son!

258
00:18:53,849 --> 00:18:56,289
She's my woman! I hit her as I like!

259
00:18:57,609 --> 00:18:58,410
Stop!

260
00:18:58,529 --> 00:18:59,369
Stay out of this.

261
00:18:59,529 --> 00:19:01,329
Be reasonable.

262
00:19:01,769 --> 00:19:02,769
Get inside.

263
00:19:03,329 --> 00:19:04,049
Get inside.

264
00:19:04,049 --> 00:19:06,049
Stop crying, or I'll beat you to death!

265
00:19:43,210 --> 00:19:43,930
How dare you!

266
00:19:45,289 --> 00:19:46,890
Do not touch the switch.

267
00:19:59,010 --> 00:20:00,129
You useless thing!

268
00:20:52,930 --> 00:20:53,930
What's your name?

269
00:20:54,970 --> 00:20:55,890
My name is Liu Mei.

270
00:20:56,769 --> 00:20:59,410
Liu Mei, can you do me a favor?

271
00:21:00,369 --> 00:21:01,609
I can't let you out.

272
00:21:01,849 --> 00:21:02,970
You're crazy.

273
00:21:03,930 --> 00:21:04,930
I didn't mean that.

274
00:21:05,529 --> 00:21:07,049
Just find me some paper

275
00:21:07,809 --> 00:21:09,329
and a pen.

276
00:21:09,730 --> 00:21:11,410
I don't know where to find them.

277
00:21:12,329 --> 00:21:14,369
I remember in a drawer,

278
00:21:15,010 --> 00:21:16,450
there's a small pencil stub.

279
00:21:17,490 --> 00:21:18,450
Bring me anything,

280
00:21:18,609 --> 00:21:19,890
as long as I can write on it.

281
00:21:19,960 --> 00:21:21,569
Please, help me, okay?

282
00:21:22,170 --> 00:21:23,849
Take the congee and pickles out.

283
00:21:24,129 --> 00:21:25,049
Give the basket back.

284
00:21:31,730 --> 00:21:32,849
Help me!

285
00:22:33,432 --> 00:22:35,896
(In 2006, I...)

286
00:22:36,369 --> 00:22:39,032
(In 2006, I was locked in the cellar.)

287
00:22:42,008 --> 00:22:43,672
(I saw sunlight at noon today)

288
00:22:44,344 --> 00:22:45,176
(just for a while.)

289
00:22:46,010 --> 00:22:48,089
(I sunned the frostbite
on my hands and feet.)

290
00:22:48,690 --> 00:22:49,569
(Spring has arrived.)

291
00:22:53,089 --> 00:22:55,010
(A dried leaf fell in today.)

292
00:22:55,769 --> 00:22:57,049
(Have the kids started school?)

293
00:22:58,329 --> 00:23:01,329
(Xiaoming and Bai Shu should be
in their final year of high school.)

294
00:23:11,769 --> 00:23:12,690
(It's raining.)

295
00:23:13,490 --> 00:23:15,289
(The rain soaked the straw mat.)

296
00:23:15,970 --> 00:23:17,650
(There might be frost tonight.)

297
00:23:24,329 --> 00:23:25,089
(Cold.)

298
00:23:26,410 --> 00:23:27,369
(So cold.)

299
00:23:34,490 --> 00:23:35,769
(I heard firecrackers.)

300
00:23:37,410 --> 00:23:38,329
(It's Spring Festival.)

301
00:23:44,824 --> 00:23:47,192
(February 17, 2007,
Chinese New Year's Eve)

302
00:24:10,690 --> 00:24:11,450
Madam.

303
00:24:12,250 --> 00:24:13,010
Liu Mei.

304
00:24:13,849 --> 00:24:15,010
I'm going into labor.

305
00:24:15,129 --> 00:24:15,690
Liu Mei.

306
00:24:17,609 --> 00:24:18,809
Liu Mei, what's wrong?

307
00:24:19,289 --> 00:24:22,049
My stomach hurts! I'm having the baby.

308
00:24:22,049 --> 00:24:23,490
Are you giving birth?

309
00:24:23,730 --> 00:24:25,730
Where's Hao Ying? Call him!

310
00:24:25,890 --> 00:24:26,970
Go to the hospital.

311
00:24:42,329 --> 00:24:44,250
Hurry! Go to the hospital!

312
00:24:44,410 --> 00:24:45,490
Just think of it

313
00:24:46,490 --> 00:24:48,609
as a good deed done by my baby and me.

314
00:24:50,529 --> 00:24:51,410
You go.

315
00:24:52,129 --> 00:24:53,010
Don't worry about me.

316
00:24:53,410 --> 00:24:55,289
Hurry up! Go to the hospital!

317
00:24:55,410 --> 00:24:55,970
Go quickly!

318
00:24:56,490 --> 00:24:57,049
Liu Mei!

319
00:24:57,129 --> 00:24:58,809
Run! Escape!

320
00:24:59,490 --> 00:25:00,088
Liu Mei!

321
00:25:01,410 --> 00:25:03,329
Liu Mei! Go to the hospital!

322
00:25:04,970 --> 00:25:05,809
It hurts so much!

323
00:25:07,250 --> 00:25:07,769
Go.

324
00:25:07,809 --> 00:25:08,440
Go!

325
00:25:08,792 --> 00:25:09,410
Go!

326
00:25:09,410 --> 00:25:10,849
Go quickly! Go!

327
00:25:11,369 --> 00:25:11,930
Go quickly!

328
00:25:13,490 --> 00:25:15,849
It hurts! Take me to the hospital!

329
00:26:04,664 --> 00:26:06,264
(Delivery Room)

330
00:26:35,416 --> 00:26:38,360
(Delivery Room)

331
00:27:02,264 --> 00:27:03,569
(Delivery Room)

332
00:27:03,569 --> 00:27:04,569
Wen Yuxiu gave birth.

333
00:27:05,410 --> 00:27:06,089
A boy?

334
00:27:06,650 --> 00:27:08,569
A girl, six jin and seven liang.

335
00:27:27,970 --> 00:27:29,289
How dare you!

336
00:27:38,168 --> 00:27:39,544
(Convenience Store, Public Phone)

337
00:27:52,408 --> 00:27:55,000
(February 18, 2007,
Chinese New Year's Day)

338
00:28:00,609 --> 00:28:01,250
Hello?

339
00:28:04,250 --> 00:28:04,809
Who is it?

340
00:28:14,329 --> 00:28:16,250
Yuxiu? Is that you? Yuxiu?

341
00:28:38,872 --> 00:28:41,528
(Convenience Store)

342
00:28:53,450 --> 00:28:55,569
Perhaps she was locked
in the cellar for too long.

343
00:28:56,089 --> 00:28:58,690
After escaping,
your mom's voice overwhelmed her.

344
00:28:59,010 --> 00:28:59,890
She lost her speech.

345
00:29:00,529 --> 00:29:02,890
So your mom only heard her breathing.

346
00:29:03,970 --> 00:29:05,890
She firmly believed Wen Yuxiu was alive.

347
00:29:07,089 --> 00:29:09,250
Fortunately,
she told us about this in time.

348
00:29:11,250 --> 00:29:12,089
What about Liu Mei?

349
00:29:12,729 --> 00:29:14,129
According to the clinic's records,

350
00:29:14,329 --> 00:29:17,089
there was one puerpera named Wen Yuxiu.

351
00:29:17,089 --> 00:29:20,029
(On the First Day of the Lunar New Year,
2007, Shabei County Clinic)

352
00:29:35,769 --> 00:29:37,049
Wen Yuxiu!

353
00:29:37,970 --> 00:29:41,089
Director! Wen Yuxiu is hemorrhaging!

354
00:29:43,490 --> 00:29:44,569
After Liu Mei died,

355
00:29:45,450 --> 00:29:47,289
Hao Ying handed Yamei over to Wen Yuxiu.

356
00:29:48,970 --> 00:29:50,369
She raised the child in the cellar.

357
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:54,250
(2007, Hao Ying's Cellar, Tubao Village)

358
00:29:54,250 --> 00:29:56,369
(This child never cried.)

359
00:29:56,849 --> 00:29:58,490
(She never spoke either.)

360
00:29:59,369 --> 00:30:01,690
(How much suffering would she endure?)

361
00:30:04,769 --> 00:30:06,010
(Without her,)

362
00:30:07,010 --> 00:30:09,410
(I wouldn't know
why I should keep living.)

363
00:30:14,569 --> 00:30:15,250
And then?

364
00:30:17,569 --> 00:30:18,690
When Yamei was three,

365
00:30:19,250 --> 00:30:20,210
Hao Ying took the child

366
00:30:20,369 --> 00:30:23,250
(2010, Hao Ying's Cellar, Tubao Village)
and everything hopeful from Wen Yuxiu.

367
00:30:24,024 --> 00:30:25,170
(The cellar was dark again.)

368
00:30:26,136 --> 00:30:27,384
(A woman who couldn't speak)

369
00:30:28,088 --> 00:30:29,368
(didn't write anymore.)

370
00:30:47,329 --> 00:30:49,410
I remember back in a writing class,

371
00:30:49,529 --> 00:30:51,250
Ms. Zhou asked a question.

372
00:30:52,569 --> 00:30:53,490
She said,

373
00:30:54,809 --> 00:30:56,569
"If a person is in darkness,

374
00:30:57,450 --> 00:30:59,410
what is the most important thing?"

375
00:31:01,210 --> 00:31:02,210
The answer is light.

376
00:31:03,809 --> 00:31:05,410
As long as a sliver of light remains,

377
00:31:06,410 --> 00:31:07,690
the soul won't be extinguished.

378
00:31:12,490 --> 00:31:14,369
Yamei was like the last ray of light

379
00:31:15,210 --> 00:31:16,410
in Ms. Zhou's life.

380
00:31:29,129 --> 00:31:31,210
Yamei was very important to Wen Yuxiu,

381
00:31:32,609 --> 00:31:34,490
but she definitely wasn't
her last ray of light.

382
00:31:37,010 --> 00:31:38,289
In that kind of environment,

383
00:31:38,849 --> 00:31:41,450
Wen Yuxiu still had
such tenacious vitality.

384
00:31:42,210 --> 00:31:44,490
It shows there was
a powerful force within her.

385
00:31:46,410 --> 00:31:48,569
If that force were the light,

386
00:31:50,089 --> 00:31:51,210
then the light

387
00:31:52,769 --> 00:31:54,369
could illuminate the entire universe.

388
00:32:16,609 --> 00:32:17,410
Come in.

389
00:32:18,010 --> 00:32:19,650
Wen Yuxiu, you have a visitor.

390
00:32:21,970 --> 00:32:23,769
Hello. May I know your name?

391
00:32:24,450 --> 00:32:25,369
I am Zhou Yun.

392
00:32:39,769 --> 00:32:40,490
Skinny.

393
00:32:48,369 --> 00:32:49,049
Skinny.

394
00:32:56,930 --> 00:32:58,089
Skinny.

395
00:33:01,210 --> 00:33:04,450
Look at me!
How come you don't recognize me?

396
00:33:11,250 --> 00:33:12,769
She suffered trauma before.

397
00:33:13,650 --> 00:33:15,010
She hasn't fully recovered yet.

398
00:33:43,849 --> 00:33:44,650
Look at me.

399
00:33:49,650 --> 00:33:50,329
Teacher.

400
00:33:51,490 --> 00:33:52,690
Ms. Zhou is here to see you.

401
00:33:54,490 --> 00:33:55,569
Teacher?

402
00:33:58,569 --> 00:34:00,450
You really became a teacher!

403
00:34:04,369 --> 00:34:05,769
I was her student.

404
00:34:06,049 --> 00:34:07,289
She was a good teacher.

405
00:34:08,970 --> 00:34:10,810
You gave her a pen.

406
00:34:11,370 --> 00:34:12,529
She later gave it to us.

407
00:34:14,970 --> 00:34:17,410
She said the pen represented courage.

408
00:34:19,569 --> 00:34:20,569
Skinny.

409
00:34:30,970 --> 00:34:32,370
Look at the clothes.

410
00:34:33,010 --> 00:34:34,970
Back then, the winter was so cold.

411
00:34:35,049 --> 00:34:36,970
You wore only this,

412
00:34:37,689 --> 00:34:39,490
standing at the factory gate.

413
00:34:39,810 --> 00:34:42,569
Do you remember?

414
00:34:43,209 --> 00:34:44,049
Skinny.

415
00:34:47,529 --> 00:34:48,410
Think carefully!

416
00:34:49,089 --> 00:34:51,569
Take a look. Look closely.

417
00:34:52,089 --> 00:34:52,770
Think!

418
00:34:56,049 --> 00:34:59,370
How did you become like this?

419
00:35:55,608 --> 00:35:57,528
(Room 3301)

420
00:36:03,129 --> 00:36:06,249
Yuxiu, do you smell it?

421
00:36:06,410 --> 00:36:08,209
I made you sweet and sour pork today.

422
00:36:09,930 --> 00:36:11,529
Help me set up the table.

423
00:36:30,129 --> 00:36:31,209
It's ready.

424
00:36:32,209 --> 00:36:33,529
Raise the bed a bit.

425
00:36:34,129 --> 00:36:35,209
Come on.

426
00:36:36,810 --> 00:36:38,529
Sweet and sour pork.

427
00:36:50,330 --> 00:36:50,890
Here.

428
00:36:52,089 --> 00:36:53,370
Come on. Try this.

429
00:36:54,410 --> 00:36:55,049
Open your mouth.

430
00:36:56,330 --> 00:36:56,850
Open wide.

431
00:36:57,290 --> 00:36:58,490
Okay, open wide.

432
00:37:02,810 --> 00:37:04,890
Take a bite of rice.

433
00:37:05,330 --> 00:37:06,330
Not too much.

434
00:37:09,290 --> 00:37:10,410
Open wide.

435
00:37:11,010 --> 00:37:11,529
Open wide.

436
00:37:17,089 --> 00:37:18,890
Have another piece of meat.

437
00:37:19,970 --> 00:37:21,129
Open wide.

438
00:37:21,370 --> 00:37:23,370
Open wider.

439
00:37:23,370 --> 00:37:24,850
Chew.

440
00:37:25,010 --> 00:37:26,529
Well done.

441
00:37:32,490 --> 00:37:34,609
Are you doing this out of guilt?

442
00:37:38,010 --> 00:37:39,249
I do feel guilty.

443
00:37:40,089 --> 00:37:41,529
But not in the way you think.

444
00:37:43,010 --> 00:37:44,850
I'm not as despicable as you think.

445
00:37:45,689 --> 00:37:47,810
You met her
when she ran away after giving birth.

446
00:37:50,649 --> 00:37:51,689
Are you interrogating me?

447
00:37:54,850 --> 00:37:56,490
I've already told the police everything.

448
00:37:58,008 --> 00:37:59,649
We ran into each other at the hospital.

449
00:38:00,850 --> 00:38:02,529
I was pregnant with Xiaofei at the time.

450
00:38:03,609 --> 00:38:05,689
She told me she was going to run.

451
00:38:07,129 --> 00:38:07,890
How did she escape?

452
00:38:11,249 --> 00:38:11,970
I don't know.

453
00:38:13,689 --> 00:38:15,770
We gave birth on the same day.

454
00:38:16,370 --> 00:38:18,089
The day after giving birth, I was dizzy.

455
00:38:18,770 --> 00:38:20,330
Then I heard she had already run away.

456
00:38:29,689 --> 00:38:30,529
You're lying again.

457
00:38:31,970 --> 00:38:33,450
She ran away wearing your clothes.

458
00:38:33,850 --> 00:38:35,370
You met her when she left.

459
00:38:36,249 --> 00:38:37,569
My clothes?

460
00:38:39,410 --> 00:38:41,089
Isn't this just a hospital gown?

461
00:38:43,770 --> 00:38:44,970
There's a heart drawn on it.

462
00:38:45,609 --> 00:38:46,930
I drew it myself.

463
00:38:52,609 --> 00:38:53,569
You misremembered it.

464
00:38:53,770 --> 00:38:54,930
No, I couldn't.

465
00:38:57,649 --> 00:38:59,049
You were three or four years old.

466
00:38:59,850 --> 00:39:01,049
What could you remember?

467
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:07,049
(Qidaohezi People's Hospital)

468
00:39:07,049 --> 00:39:10,010
One day, grandma took me
to the hospital to see you.

469
00:39:10,689 --> 00:39:13,209
When we entered the ward,
we saw you sitting on the windowsill.

470
00:39:14,089 --> 00:39:15,209
I was only four years old.

471
00:39:15,850 --> 00:39:17,249
I didn't know what suicide meant.

472
00:39:18,609 --> 00:39:19,850
I was terrified that day.

473
00:39:23,010 --> 00:39:23,810
I was thinking

474
00:39:25,770 --> 00:39:26,970
that if you really jumped,

475
00:39:28,010 --> 00:39:29,010
I would lose you.

476
00:39:31,850 --> 00:39:34,209
So I drew a heart on your gown.

477
00:39:36,209 --> 00:39:37,410
I wanted you to know

478
00:39:40,609 --> 00:39:41,689
that no matter what,

479
00:39:44,850 --> 00:39:45,970
at least you had me.

480
00:39:49,209 --> 00:39:50,529
So I couldn't misremember it.

481
00:39:57,770 --> 00:39:59,290
You still remember that?

482
00:40:04,129 --> 00:40:05,089
Are you admitting it?

483
00:40:10,609 --> 00:40:11,249
Sure.

484
00:40:12,649 --> 00:40:15,290
She came to my ward the day she ran.

485
00:40:16,490 --> 00:40:18,290
To stop her from running away,

486
00:40:18,490 --> 00:40:20,529
Hao Ying took all her clothes
from the hospital.

487
00:40:21,850 --> 00:40:23,649
She could only run in her hospital gown.

488
00:40:24,569 --> 00:40:27,490
I saw blood on her gown. It was dirty.

489
00:40:28,450 --> 00:40:29,930
So I gave her mine.

490
00:40:31,970 --> 00:40:32,850
Then she ran.

491
00:40:34,049 --> 00:40:35,129
What were you thinking?

492
00:40:37,410 --> 00:40:39,209
It was only her second day
after giving birth!

493
00:40:40,970 --> 00:40:42,129
And you just let her go?

494
00:40:42,330 --> 00:40:43,169
What should I do?

495
00:40:43,689 --> 00:40:44,649
She had to run.

496
00:40:46,370 --> 00:40:49,169
Should I have let her go back
with Hao Ying and get beaten to death?

497
00:40:51,096 --> 00:40:52,089
Did you give her money?

498
00:40:58,970 --> 00:40:59,850
What's wrong?

499
00:41:00,410 --> 00:41:01,089
Nothing.

500
00:41:04,529 --> 00:41:05,850
I had no money.

501
00:41:09,930 --> 00:41:11,450
You didn't give her any?

502
00:41:14,450 --> 00:41:15,129
Mom.

503
00:41:16,649 --> 00:41:17,850
When you went south,

504
00:41:18,569 --> 00:41:20,290
she gave you all her savings.

505
00:41:20,689 --> 00:41:21,970
When she felt helpless,

506
00:41:24,450 --> 00:41:25,450
what did you give her?

507
00:41:26,370 --> 00:41:27,770
You didn't give her money,

508
00:41:28,569 --> 00:41:30,089
but just a hospital gown?

509
00:41:36,209 --> 00:41:37,850
Xiaofei was born in August.

510
00:41:37,850 --> 00:41:38,890
It was summer then.

511
00:41:40,209 --> 00:41:42,010
Ms. Zhou left in the summer too.

512
00:41:42,689 --> 00:41:44,770
She was found at the factory in winter.

513
00:41:46,290 --> 00:41:47,770
She had left for a long time.

514
00:41:48,450 --> 00:41:49,609
It was freezing.

515
00:41:51,169 --> 00:41:53,010
And she only wore one hospital gown.

516
00:41:56,569 --> 00:41:58,169
Did you know she was deathly ill?

517
00:42:00,569 --> 00:42:02,370
How did she survive those months?

518
00:42:14,089 --> 00:42:15,850
When she left,
didn't you think about it?

519
00:42:17,089 --> 00:42:18,410
Didn't you think she might die?

520
00:42:28,569 --> 00:42:29,930
What a great friend you are.

521
00:42:55,410 --> 00:42:56,850
Aren't you going to ask me

522
00:42:56,850 --> 00:43:00,450
why I wanted to die back then?

523
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:12,808
=Vanished Name=
